(27, 'Odisha govt gives protection to forest officials u/s-197 of CrPC', 6, 8, '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Bhubaneswar, July 5 (IANS) Following the killing of two forest officials by poachers in Similipal Tiger Reserve (STR), the state government has provided protection to forest officials under section 197 of Code of Criminal Procedure (CrPC).</span><br></p>', '2023-07-05 10:27:08', NULL, 1, 'Odisha-govt-gives-protection-to-forest-officials-u/s-197-of-CrPC', '6b193292de587a3637ddc96582435cea.jpg', 0),
(28, 'Bihar minister not happy with Education dept Secy’s decision on cut in grant', 6, 8, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Patna, July 5 (IANS) After Bihar education Minister Prof. Chandrashekher,&nbsp;&nbsp;SC-ST minister Ratnesh Sada has expressed dissatisfaction over the recent move of additional Chief Secretary K.K. Pathak&nbsp; to reduce the grant to the Mahadalit Tola Sewak by 25 per cent.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">As per the fresh guidelines passed by the additional chief secretary, there is a provision to cut the grant of Mahadalit Tola Sewak by 25 per cent if the attendance of students is not 90 per cent in the schools, and the responsibility of maintaining the attendance is on the sewaks .</p>', '2023-07-05 10:29:26', NULL, 1, 'Bihar-minister-not-happy-with-Education-dept-Secy’s-decision-on-cut-in-grant', '494ce890a0d155b77f9561b60265c009.jpg', 0),
(29, 'Telangana HC completes hearing on PIL on land allotment to director Shankar', 7, 9, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Hyderabad, July 5 (IANS) The Telangana High Court has completed the hearing on PIL challenging land allotment to well-known film director N. Shankar and posted the case for orders on July 7.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The state government had allotted 5 acres of land to the director at Mokila village in Rangareddy district near Hyderabad in 2019 for setting up a film studio. The land allotment to the director was challenged through a Public Interest Litigation (PIL).</p>', '2023-07-05 10:31:41', NULL, 1, 'Telangana-HC-completes-hearing-on-PIL-on-land-allotment-to-director-Shankar', '76919230dfb9cc4e634995e67c3ead34.jpg', 0),
(30, 'Gujarat among India’s top 10 states in deposits per capita', 4, 13, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">As of March 31, 2023, the state’s deposits per capita stood at Rs 97,000, positioning it as the ninth-highest among the major states in the country.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">While several smaller states and union territories boast higher per capita deposits, Gujarat holds a respectable position among its major counterparts.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Gujarat generally exhibits a higher level of financial literacy, and a significant portion of the public’s wealth is also invested in other asset classes such as equities, mutual funds, and bullion. This may explain the relatively lower per capita deposits in ban</p>', '2023-07-05 10:37:53', NULL, 1, 'Gujarat-among-India’s-top-10-states-in-deposits-per-capita', '90c352f3f7fa60214f7b925e56fb6f5c.jpg', 0),
(31, 'DGCA, EASA join hands to propel unmanned aircraft systems, air mobility', 4, 13, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The MoU was signed in Brussels on Tuesday.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">In a statement, the Ministry said that this collaboration would include cooperation between DGCA and EASA in the areas of development of certification standards and environmental standards and related requirements for the certification and use of unmanned aircraft systems and innovative air mobility operations which includes licensing of personnel, training, air traffic management and infrastructure, including Unmanned Aircraft System Traffic Management (UTM) standards and services.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">“The MoU will also ensure regular information sharing between the two authorities on the technological developments and research in this area and also their respective strategies for outreach to relevant stakeholders. Further, the MoU will result in collaboration in conducting conferences, workshops, training programmers by DGCA and EASA in this area,” it said.</p>', '2023-07-05 10:39:54', NULL, 1, 'DGCA,-EASA-join-hands-to-propel-unmanned-aircraft-systems,-air-mobility', '431e7de14494fdaa1bcef4fd664ea7b9.jpg', 0),
(32, 'RIL stock has historically outperformed going into AGM', 4, 13, '<p data-mce-style=\"font-weight: 400;\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">“We expect similar announcements this year, especially around Jio Financial Services (JFS), clean energy and digital business. RIL stock has historically outperformed going into the AGM on most instances”, the report said.</p><p data-mce-style=\"font-weight: 400;\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">RIL is in the new list of 10 quarterly stock recommendations among Asia Pac companies based on the view that these stocks could have the most significant market and business-related catalysts in the quarter ahead, BofA said.</p><p data-mce-style=\"font-weight: 400;\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">On the listing of JFS, the report said RIL has indicated that they intend to spin-off the financial services arm and have already indicated the demerger process. By separating financial services from the core business, RIL appears to be keeping arm’s length transaction from other entities, and in theory helping them better to attract strategic or JV partners who are keen only in financial services arm-like what they did with Jio or tower InvIT. Media articles indicate that listing may happen by Sept-Oct 23.</p>', '2023-07-05 10:41:39', NULL, 1, 'RIL-stock-has-historically-outperformed-going-into-AGM', 'aad9019241e204dbeb7597f0f9678949.jpg', 0),
(33, 'Economic fundamentals don’t warrant continuation of stock market rally beyond current levels: Analysts', 4, 13, '<p data-mce-style=\"font-weight: 400;\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">V.K. Vijayakumar, Chief Investment Strategist at Geojit Financial Services, said the 15 per cent surge in Nifty from the low levels of March has given a bullish flavour to this rally; but it is difficult to describe this as a bull market since valuations do not permit a sustained rally and the evolving economic fundamentals do not warrant continuation of the rally much beyond the current levels.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"></p><p data-mce-style=\"font-weight: 400;\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">A sustained bull run needs low valuations and steadily improving growth and earnings prospects. Valuations are not favourable now and growth and earnings prospects, though good, are not very bright, he said</p>', '2023-07-05 10:46:10', NULL, 1, 'Economic-fundamentals-don’t-warrant-continuation-of-stock-market-rally-beyond-current-levels:-Analysts', 'b70aa34856acc0f59c767ffbec8e0914.jpg', 7),
(34, 'Dibrugarh-bound IndiGo flight aborts take off due to technical glitch', 4, 13, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">According to Airport Authority of India (AAI) sources here, the pilot noticed the glitch while the aircraft was taxing the runway.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">State Ministers Ranjeet Das, Bimal Bora and Congress leader Romen Barthakur were on board flight and heading towards Dibrugarh for individual programs.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">An inspection to repair the glitch is currently under</p>', '2023-07-05 10:49:45', NULL, 1, 'Dibrugarh-bound-IndiGo-flight-aborts-take-off-due-to-technical-glitch', 'e3a2d8a866db06b8162ce53777a39db6.jpg', 0),
(35, 'Goalkeeper Gurpreet Singh Sandhu shines in shootout as India clinch SAFF Championship against Kuwait', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">India had been taken into deep waters over the past four days. More than 240 minutes of physically gruelling football against two good teams in Kuwait and Lebanon. And penalty shootouts were needed to decide these intense games.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Enter Gurpreet Singh Sandhu.</p><p class=\"no_first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The SAFF Championship on the line, the Bengaluru FC goalkeeper guessed correctly, dove to his left, and stopped Kuwait captain Khaled Hajiah’s spot kick and for the second time in four days, won India a penalty shootout – this time for the team’s second trophy in two weeks.</p>', '2023-07-05 10:53:10', NULL, 1, 'Goalkeeper-Gurpreet-Singh-Sandhu-shines-in-shootout-as-India-clinch-SAFF-Championship-against-Kuwait', '14dab36b2a2a8bc79a449b31b6ee1d73.jpg', 0),
(36, 'Ajit Agarkar appointed chief selector with promise of pay hike', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The Board of Control for Cricket in India (BCCI) has appointed Ajit Agarkar as chairman of the Senior Men’s Selection Committee.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The BCCI, in a press release, announced that its Cricket Advisory Committee (CAC) consisting of Sulakshana Naik, Ashok Malhotra and Jatin Paranjape recommended Agarkar for the position of selector in the men’s selection committee.</p>', '2023-07-05 10:54:09', NULL, 1, 'Ajit-Agarkar-appointed-chief-selector-with-promise-of-pay-hike', 'dfd256440bff52a0a7c55ae72b1ecdfb.jpg', 0),
(37, 'Another World Cup miss but for Zimbabwe Cricket, winning may not be the only thing that matters', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Some 7,800 miles away from England – where a strong case for winning not being the only thing that matters in sport has been made over the past couple of weeks – in the city of Bulawayo, a defeat doesn’t completely feel like one. Five wins were followed by two defeats, and that was that. Zimbabwe will not be playing in the ODI World Cup for a second time in four years. An absence for only a second occasion since they made their tournament debut all the way back in 1983. A defeat to Scotland in the qualifying fixture on Tuesday sealed their fate. Five years back, when the nation hosted the qualifiers for the 2019 World Cup, Godwin Mamhiyo was there to witness another heartbreak, as he was on Tuesday.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">“We were there, the whole union, when we lost to the UAE,” he tells&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Indian Express</em>, further describing a set of adjectives thoroughly applicable following their most recent outing. “It was shattering, heartbreaking. I’m talking about people who are passionate about this game, people that break down crying when things go wrong. It was a difficult period for Zimbabwe cricket as well as the fans.”</p>', '2023-07-05 10:55:10', NULL, 1, 'Another-World-Cup-miss-but-for-Zimbabwe-Cricket,-winning-may-not-be-the-only-thing-that-matters', 'a5e783327109a9f41292e85193ef46f6.jpg', 0),
(38, 'Is it the end of James Anderson in an alien bouncer-happy world?', 1, 14, '<p>IT<span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">’s funny how this Ashes has free-balled into a quirky world of its own. It’s not England’s bazball, it’s not Australia’s rope-a-dope professionalism but an injury to a spinner that pushed it into an unknown space. When Nathan Lyon hurt his calf, the repercussions couldn’t be predicted. But now, it has had both countries’ pacers going hammer and tongs, willing their shoulders and backs to keep hurling short-pitched stuff for hours together.</span></p>', '2023-07-05 10:56:27', NULL, 1, 'Is-it-the-end-of-James-Anderson-in-an-alien-bouncer-happy-world?', '07985258b5820d2935b69270a422ef16.jpg', 0),
(39, '‘In the company of greatness’: Watch Virat Kohli, Rohit Sharma meet Sir Garfield Sobers', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The Indian cricket team is scheduled to tour the West Indies in July and August 2023 for a two-Test, three-ODI, and five-T20I series.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">But before that, skipper Rohit Sharma and premier batter Virat Kohli met Windies great Sir Garfield Sobers.</p><p class=\"no_first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Sobers had his wife by his side and the clip has gone viral on social media.</p><p><ev-engagement group-name=\"contentLogin\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"></ev-engagement><ev-engagement group-name=\"myNotification\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"></ev-engagement></p><div class=\"ev-meter-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"><div class=\"ie-int-campign-ad\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;\"></div><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Incidentally in 2020, Kohli was awarded with the Sir Garfield Sobers Award for male cricketer of the decade.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">India head coach&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/about/rahul-dravid/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Rahul Dravid</a>&nbsp;can also be seen interacting with Sobers and introducing Shubman Gill as ‘one of our most exciting batter’.</p></div>', '2023-07-05 10:58:09', NULL, 1, '‘In-the-company-of-greatness’:-Watch-Virat-Kohli,-Rohit-Sharma-meet-Sir-Garfield-Sobers', 'a29daad5de29b71b171c87b04ce59113.jpg', 0),
(40, '‘Virat Kohli said something and it brought the best out of him’: Joe Root says Jonny Bairstow is ready to take his anger out on Australia', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The stumping of Jonny Bairstow by Alex Carey in the 2nd Ashes Test at Lord’s has left the Englishman frustrated and according to his England teammate Joe Root, Bairstow is in the mood to put things in their right place when the two teams collide at Headingley.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">“You can bet your bottom dollar he will have the bit between his teeth. I don’t think he took it great. I don’t think anyone would, would they”” said Root.</p><p class=\"no_first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">“He does thrive off things like this. You will be able to spot his mood a mile off.”</p><p><ev-engagement group-name=\"contentLogin\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"></ev-engagement><ev-engagement group-name=\"myNotification\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"></ev-engagement></p><div class=\"ev-meter-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"><div class=\"ie-int-campign-ad\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;\"></div><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Recalling an incident in a match against India in 2022, Root said, “Go back to Edgbaston last year. Someone said something to him – I think it was&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/about/virat-kohli/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Virat Kohli</a>&nbsp;– and it brought the best out of him. Let’s hope that happens again.”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Kohli and Bairstow were involved in verbal battles. Bairstow was on 13 off 60, when the verbal interaction with Kohli happened. He shifted gears and galloped to his third consecutive Test hundred in 119 balls.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">“There is always something like this in these big series and this one would have to involve Jonny,” Root added.</p></div>', '2023-07-05 11:20:53', NULL, 1, '‘Virat-Kohli-said-something-and-it-brought-the-best-out-of-him’:-Joe-Root-says-Jonny-Bairstow-is-ready-to-take-his-anger-out-on-Australia', 'a2320aa55748a95884d1111bd2d64886.jpg', 0),
(41, '‘My experience is when people don’t like a dismissal…’: Legendary umpire Simon Taufel on Jonny Bairstow controversy', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The stumping of Jonny Bairstow by Alex Carey in the 2nd Ashes Test at Lord’s has been the talk of the town.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">This was after Bairstow was given out stumped after he wandered out of his crease.</p><p class=\"no_first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The decision was sent upstairs and third umpire, Marais Erasmus, ruled the England gloveman as stumped.</p><p><ev-engagement group-name=\"contentLogin\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"></ev-engagement><ev-engagement group-name=\"myNotification\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\"></ev-engagement></p><div class=\"ev-meter-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"><div class=\"ie-int-campign-ad\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;\"></div><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Speaking on the incident, former legendary umpire Simon Taufel backed the third umpire’s decision to give Bairstow out and stated that the ball is not considered to be “dead” till the time both the teams regard it as “out of play”.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">“Correct decision made. They (England) just didn’t like it. For that ball to be considered dead after the over or even after the delivery, both sides need to disregard it is in play. Clearly, the fielding side hadn’t,” Taufel told ABC Sydney Mornings.</p></div>', '2023-07-05 11:22:33', NULL, 1, '‘My-experience-is-when-people-don’t-like-a-dismissal…’:-Legendary-umpire-Simon-Taufel-on-Jonny-Bairstow-controversy', 'a2320aa55748a95884d1111bd2d64886.jpg', 0),
(42, '‘He often uses abusive language on the field’: Ishant Sharma on MS Dhoni', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Former Indian fast bowler Ishant Sharma revealed that India’s World Cup-winning captain MS Dhoni has many strengths but calm and cool isn’t one of them and the former Indian skipper often used abusive language on the field.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Speaking on the TRS Clips Youtube channel Ishant said, “Mahi bhai has many strengths. But calm and cool aren’t one of them. He often uses abusive language on the field, and I’ve heard it firsthand.”</p><p class=\"no_first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">“Whether it’s during the IPL or with the Indian team, people are always around him. You’ll find someone or the other sitting with Mahi bhai. It’s like the feeling of being in a village, just missing the trees,” he added.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:23:26', NULL, 1, '‘He-often-uses-abusive-language-on-the-field’:-Ishant-Sharma-on-MS-Dhoni', '80ac1ba1504c2400a4db665aaa19e71a.jpg', 0),
(43, 'After Babe Ruth, the Japanese Shohei Ohtani becomes baseball’s first two-way player in 100 years', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Recently, the United States of America and Japan met in the final of the World Baseball Classic Final. Japan narrowly edged out the USA and signalled yet another time that the Japanese – a baseball-mad nation by its own right, had arrived on the grand stage. And a once-in-a-generation star athlete in Shohei Ohtani led them to the promised land.</p><div><br></div>', '2023-07-05 11:24:32', NULL, 1, 'After-Babe-Ruth,-the-Japanese-Shohei-Ohtani-becomes-baseball’s-first-two-way-player-in-100-years', '9ae8368e37140a97c5fe93b243e05b40.jpg', 0),
(44, 'Lust Stories 2: In appreciation of Tamannaah and Vijay Varma’s Sex with the Ex, the ugly duckling of Netflix’s anthology', 2, 12, '<p>F<span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">rom the first frames of Sex with the Ex, director Sujoy Ghosh’s wickedly entertaining segment in the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/lust-stories-bhumi-pednekar-best-performance-zoya-akhtar-netflix-film-8033576/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Netflix anthology</a></span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Lust Stories 2, it is made explicitly clear that we aren’t in the ‘real world’. Vijay Varma’s character is racing along a scenic highway in a vintage Mercedes, having a saucy FaceTime session with the mistress that he is about to have a liaison with. Is this, perhaps, what the movie is going to be about? Not at all. What we’re about to watch instead is a darkly humorous satire complete with a murder plot, a secret pregnancy, and several sepia-toned flashbacks.</span></p>', '2023-07-05 11:26:10', NULL, 1, 'Lust-Stories-2:-In-appreciation-of-Tamannaah-and-Vijay-Varma’s-Sex-with-the-Ex,-the-ugly-duckling-of-Netflix’s-anthology', 'b66cf9f896c0e057928081a109fd3b8b.png', 0);
