(45, '30 years of Hum Hain Rahi Pyar Ke: Aamir Khan felt he looked ‘harassed’ in the film, didn’t understand the character even after film released', 1, 14, '<p><br></p><div class=\"audio-player-tts-sec ev-meter-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; height: 61px; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"><div class=\"audio-player-tts\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative;\"><div class=\"audio-player-group\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; align-items: center;\"><input type=\"range\" id=\"seek-slider\" max=\"4000\" value=\"0\" aria-label=\"Article Audio progress bar\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; appearance: none; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(rgb(255, 0, 0), rgb(255, 0, 0)) 0% 0% / 0% 0% no-repeat rgb(226, 226, 226); border-radius: 5px; width: 425.275px;\"><div class=\"audio-time audio-duration\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; column-gap: 20px; line-height: 16px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; align-items: center;\"><span id=\"current-time\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">00:00</span><div id=\"audio-player-speed\" data-speed=\"1.0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px 2px 3px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex; min-width: 100px; height: 24px; border-radius: 12px; background-color: rgb(226, 226, 226);\"><span class=\"speed-options active\" data-speed=\"1.0\" style=\"margin: 0px 2px 0px 0px; padding: 2px 8px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; width: fit-content; height: 20px; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1x</span><span class=\"speed-options\" data-speed=\"1.5\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 8px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; width: fit-content; height: 20px; border-radius: 10px;\">1.5x</span><span class=\"speed-options\" data-speed=\"1.8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 8px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; cursor: pointer; width: fit-content; height: 20px; border-radius: 10px;\">1.8x</span></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"pcl-full-content\" class=\"story_details\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 28px;\">Aamir Khan and Juhi Chawla starrer Hum Hain Rahi Pyar Ke released in theaters 30 years ago and became one of the most popular comedies of the time. Directed by&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/mahesh-bhatt-calls-aamir-khan-a-victim-of-his-idea-of-perfection-8181073/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Mahesh Bhatt,</a>&nbsp;</span>the film had&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/aamir-khan-insecure-about-height-rani-mukerji-8696835/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Aamir</a>&nbsp;</span>playing a reserved man who has now gotten the responsibility of his deceased sister’s kids. When Juhi’s character enters their home, she, along with the kids infuse joy in his life. Juhi got a lot of acclaim for her performance in the film, and even the film got two National Awards – Special Jury Award to director Mahesh Bhatt and Best Female Playback Singer to Alka Yagnik for ‘Ghunghat Ki Aad Se’.</p></div>', '2023-07-05 11:27:12', NULL, 1, '30-years-of-Hum-Hain-Rahi-Pyar-Ke:-Aamir-Khan-felt-he-looked-‘harassed’-in-the-film,-didn’t-understand-the-character-even-after-film-released', '667019d2ca4e4d56dc41dbfbc96cd180.jpg', 0),
(46, 'Deepika Padukone and Kusha Kapila recreate Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani’s iconic scene, watch', 2, 12, '<p>A<span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">ctor Deepika Padukone has tapped into social media influencer and comedienne Kusha Kapila’s potential for the promotion of her skincare brand. The two artists have come together for a special video, to recreate a special scene from Deepika’s 2013 film Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani.</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The 2013 film starred Deepika and Ranbir Kapoor in lead roles. The scene the actor recreated with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/web-series/kusha-kapila-announces-separation-from-husband-zorawar-ahluwalia-8687450/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Kusha</a>&nbsp;originally features Deepika, Ranbir, and Rana Daggubati, who had made a cameo in the film. Kusha recently announced her separation from husband Zorawar.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:28:16', NULL, 1, 'Deepika-Padukone-and-Kusha-Kapila-recreate-Yeh-Jawaani-Hai-Deewani’s-iconic-scene,-watch', '2a8428339f94e44465077af1d82c3820.jpg', 0),
(47, 'When Aishwarya Rai gave a fitting reply to British interviewer who said, ‘You are encouraging men to ogle at women in swimsuits’', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Aishwarya Rai became a popular face not just in India but across the world after winning the Miss World title held at Sun City, South Africa in 1994. But during one of her interviews in the West, she was told by a reporter that the beauty pageants are ‘encouraging men to ogle at women in swimsuits’. The actor reasoned that all that happens at the beauty pageants is to raise funds for charitable organisations. However, later she only<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/when-aishwarya-rai-spoke-against-bikini-round-in-miss-world-pageant-cancelled-it-next-year-different-nationalities-uncomfortable-8327510/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;spoke against the bikini round</span></a>&nbsp;in these competitions.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">During her appearance on the British TV show, ‘The Morning’, Aishwarya was told by the host, “Whatever the reasons be, you are encouraging men to sit in front of television and ogling and look at the pretty bodies in swimsuits.”</p>', '2023-07-05 11:29:33', NULL, 1, 'When-Aishwarya-Rai-gave-a-fitting-reply-to-British-interviewer-who-said,-‘You-are-encouraging-men-to-ogle-at-women-in-swimsuits’', 'd0f8537f7656051016045b5835ca0233.jpg', 0),
(48, 'Vidya Balan says she’s ‘little bit nervous’ about returning to theatres after 4 years, box office pressure: ‘People have expectations’', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Actor&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/vidya-balan-would-go-to-a-sai-baba-temple-alone-at-night-and-ask-why-god-was-punishing-her-8755635/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Vidya Balan</a>&nbsp;promoted her upcoming whodunit Neeyat in Mumbai on Wednesday. Here, the actor spoke about returning to the big screen after a gap of four years. She was last seen in Jagan Shakti’s Mission Mangal with Akshay Kumar and Taapsee Pannu, among others.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">At the press conference, Vidya was asked if she is nervous as she is returning to the big screen after a long gap and if the pressure of the film’s box-office numbers bogs her down. Confessing that she is a “little bit” nervous, Vidya said, “I think I always feel excited and nervous and I can’t tell the difference at all, it feels all the same a few days before release. I like the fact that people have expectations from this film and from me, I am very grateful for that. I am very hopeful that everyone will enjoy it.”</p>', '2023-07-05 11:30:51', NULL, 1, 'Vidya-Balan-says-she’s-‘little-bit-nervous’-about-returning-to-theatres-after-4-years,-box-office-pressure:-‘People-have-expectations’', '45282bd21def53c7b2c5f436b9bfe13c.jpg', 0),
(49, 'Shah Rukh Khan’s Jawan, Dunki’ satellite and digital rights sold for Rs 480 cr: report', 1, 14, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Actor Shah Rukh Khan’s upcoming films Jawan and Dunki already seem to be making records even before their theatrical releases. The films’ digital and satellite rights are expected to be sold for Rs 480 crore, a milestone for the actor.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/shah-rukh-khan-explains-the-meaning-of-dunki-says-the-film-is-about-people-who-want-to-come-back-home-8302784/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Shah Rukh</a>&nbsp;will be seen doing intense action in Tamil filmmaker Atlee’s maiden pan-India venture Jawan. The film is slated to release on September 7. In Rajkumar Hirani’s Dunki, the actor will be part of a story that is expected to highlight the rampant use of an illegal backdoor route called ‘Donkey Flight’ by Indians to migrate to countries like Canada and the USA.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:31:34', NULL, 1, 'Shah-Rukh-Khan’s-Jawan,-Dunki’-satellite-and-digital-rights-sold-for-Rs-480-cr:-report', '893cd037bbf5b0bb906af9483a182978.jpg', 0),
(50, 'As NCP splits, Congress eyes bigger role in Maharashtra politics', 3, 4, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">While Maharashtra Congress leaders on Tuesday made it a point to extend solidarity to&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/sharad-pawar-hits-ground-running-to-build-something-new-8699429/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">NCP president Sharad Pawar</a></span>, the party also emphasised that it is time to grow bigger in the state.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Senior Congress leader and former CM Ashok Chavan said the space that has become vacant after&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/after-split-the-war-ajits-mlas-with-me-vs-uncles-people-with-us-8698024/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Ajit Pawar’s rebellion</a></span>&nbsp;gives an opportunity to the Congress. “The Congress now has scope to grow — a scope to contest more seats,” he said.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:33:20', NULL, 1, 'As-NCP-splits,-Congress-eyes-bigger-role-in-Maharashtra-politics', '878c61b8538a7cea6e20cbb3598bad25.jpg', 0),
(51, 'Splits to purges: In Pawar-Ajit battle for control over NCP, an echo of Uddhav-Shinde’s Sena war', 3, 4, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The raging power tussle in Maharashtra between&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/pune/sharad-pawar-on-ajit-pawar-rebellion-five-key-points-8697740/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Nationalist Congress Party (NCP) chief Sharad Pawar</span></a>&nbsp;and senior party leader and his nephew Ajit Pawar seems to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/ajit-pawar-is-deputy-cm-eight-ncp-mlas-join-bjp-sena-govt-nationalist-congress-party-8697958/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">mirror the conflict roiling the Shiv Sena</span></a>&nbsp;for the last one year.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/political-pulse/ncp-rise-stalled-ajit-pawar-reverse-card-splits-party-2019-rerun-8697275/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Ajit split the NCP to join the Eknath Shinde Sena-BJP government</span></a>&nbsp;along with eight senior party MLAs on July 2,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/ajit-pawar-rebellion-sharad-pawar-timeline-of-events-8697524/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">getting sworn in as the Deputy Chief Minister</span></a>&nbsp;— the second one after the saffron party’s Devendra Fadnavis.</p><p class=\"first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">A year ago,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/political-pulse/who-is-eknath-shinde-maharashtra-shiv-sena-thackeray-mva-7981562/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Eknath Shinde</a>&nbsp;had rebelled against the then Uddhav Thackeray-led undivided Sena and led his breakaway faction to align with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/about/bjp/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">BJP</a>&nbsp;and form their coalition government, with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/political-pulse/one-year-of-shinde-fadnavis-a-bumpy-ride-set-to-get-bumpier-8693073/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Shinde taking oath as the CM</span></a>&nbsp;despite the BJP being the senior partner.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:34:10', NULL, 1, 'Splits-to-purges:-In-Pawar-Ajit-battle-for-control-over-NCP,-an-echo-of-Uddhav-Shinde’s-Sena-war', '179530884c86e62ebb9be245326ea1b8.jpg', 0),
(52, 'Babulal Marandi interview: ‘Don’t think tribals will give JMM another chance … We’ll work to confront the ruling coalition’', 3, 4, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">The first chief minister of Jharkhand and currently the Leader of the Opposition in the state,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/political-pulse/in-jharkhand-bjp-returns-to-babulal-marandi-hopes-to-woo-tribals-back-8753220/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Babulal Marandi was named the Jharkhand BJP president</a></span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;on Tuesday. In an interview to&nbsp;</span><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif;\">The Indian Express</em><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">, he says he will work as per his “intellectual and physical capacity” for the betterment of the state and will work on a war footing for the Lok Sabha elections scheduled next year.</span><br></p>', '2023-07-05 11:39:21', NULL, 1, 'Babulal-Marandi-interview:-‘Don’t-think-tribals-will-give-JMM-another-chance-…-We’ll-work-to-confront-the-ruling-coalition’', '00760111cc44cb124994aa1985eff25e.jpg', 0),
(53, 'Sunil Jakhar, BJP’s Punjab plan lynchpin and chief: Seasoned Jat leader, ex-state Cong head', 3, 4, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">While effecting organisational changes in the run-up to the 2024 Lok Sabha polls, the BJP leadership Tuesday appointed&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/chandigarh/sunil-jakhar-named-new-punjab-bjp-chief-replaces-ashwani-sharma-8739560/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Sunil Jakhar as the new Punjab party unit president</span></a>. The former Punjab Pradesh Congress Committee (PPCC) chief, Jakhar replaced Ashwani Sharma in his new position in the state BJP. Sharma had been the saffron party chief in the state for consecutive two times.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">In May last year, three months after the Congress debacle in the Punjab Assembly polls,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/political-pulse/former-punjab-cong-chief-sunil-jakhar-now-central-to-bjp-plans-in-state-8195673/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Jakhar had switched to the BJP</span></a>&nbsp;following a spell of bad blood with the leadership of the grand old party with whom his family had decades of association. That the 69-year-old Jakhar is central to the BJP’s plans for Punjab was evident when he was inducted as a member into the BJP National Executive in December last year along with ex-Punjab chief minister Captain Amarinder Singh.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:46:59', NULL, 1, 'Sunil-Jakhar,-BJP’s-Punjab-plan-lynchpin-and-chief:-Seasoned-Jat-leader,-ex-state-Cong-head', 'ed0bf63c974bf873e9a93b864cf22d17.jpg', 0),
(54, 'In Jharkhand, BJP returns to Babulal Marandi, hopes to woo tribals back', 3, 4, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">A year to go for the Assembly elections in Jharkhand, the BJP has gone back to Babulal Marandi as the head of its state unit. The first Chief Minister of Jharkhand, who is currently the leader of its Legislature Party, the 64-year-old replaces Rajya Sabha MP Deepak Prakash.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Having parted ways with the BJP in 2002, after he had to step down as CM, Marandi returned only in early 2020, merging the party founded by him, Jharkhand Vikas Morcha (Prajatantrik), with the BJP.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:49:12', NULL, 1, 'In-Jharkhand,-BJP-returns-to-Babulal-Marandi,-hopes-to-woo-tribals-back', 'aa9ad7890a7be6778c5d0aa3baa19956.jpg', 0),
(55, 'Chronic traumatic encephalopathy diagnosed in woman athlete for the first time; know more about the brain disease', 5, 3, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The world’s first diagnosis of chronic traumatic encephalopathy (CTE) in a deceased woman athlete has come to light. A study on Heather Anderson’s brain, an Australian rules footballer who took her own life last year aged 28, indicates a degenerative&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/health/bruce-willis-frontotemporal-dementia-causes-symptoms-treatment-8450560/\" class=\"\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">brain disease</a></span>, linked to contact sports, reported&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">BBC</em>. Notably, such studies are usually carried out on male athletes.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">According to the&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">BBC</em>&nbsp;report, scientists say the case could be “the tip of the iceberg” for women in sports.</p><p class=\"first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Anderson’s family reportedly donated her brain for the study to the Australian Sports Brain Bank.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:51:32', NULL, 1, 'Chronic-traumatic-encephalopathy-diagnosed-in-woman-athlete-for-the-first-time;-know-more-about-the-brain-disease', '483abc8d593ea301a23858312dc43ed2.jpg', 0),
(56, 'Energise yourself with these foods and say goodbye to midday slump', 5, 6, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Do you always find your energy levels dropping in the afternoon, commonly known as the afternoon slump? Well, you are not alone. But did you know certain food items can help you manage this decline in energy levels. Afternoon slump refers to a period of decreased energy and alertness that typically occurs in the afternoon, usually around 2-3 p.m. It is a common experience for many people and is often associated with feelings of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/health/tired-sluggish-lifestyle-changes-health-8208652/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">fatigue</span></a>, drowsiness, difficulty concentrating, and a decline in overall productivity.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Taking to Instagram, dietician Lovneet Batra wrote, “If you are looking to avoid daytime fatigue and boost your energy levels, incorporating the right foods into your diet can make a significant difference”</p>', '2023-07-05 11:52:25', NULL, 1, 'Energise-yourself-with-these-foods-and-say-goodbye-to-midday-slump', 'c87df68c2c04c643e32555d3e6bec0ed.jpg', 0),
(57, 'Experts on how water intake affects uric acid levels in the body', 5, 6, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">A less commonly spoken health risk among those associated with lack of adequate water intake is less&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/health/foods-lower-high-uric-acid-levels-bananas-coffee-amla-cherries-yoghurt-8638404/\" class=\"\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">uric acid levels</a></span>&nbsp;in the body. Notably, while uric acid is a waste product, produced during the breakdown of various foods and drinks, its production too affects your&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/health/tips-increase-daily-consumption-water-health-drinking-water-8007008/\" class=\"\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">health</a></span>.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">“Normally, uric acid dissolves in the blood and is discarded by the kidneys through urine. But in some cases, the body produces excess uric acid or the kidney dysfunction doesn’t excrete the required amount of uric acid, resulting in hyperuricemia. Long-term hyperuricemia can lead to development of gout, a painful form of arthritis, or kidney stones,” Dr Avanish Arora, director – Urology and Uro-Oncology &amp; Senior Consultant – Robotic Urology, Nanavati Max Super Specialty Hospital, Mumbai told&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">indianexpress.com</em>.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:54:58', NULL, 1, 'Experts-on-how-water-intake-affects-uric-acid-levels-in-the-body', '4f0961f59c7bc805bfcc5bd615fc8b76.jpg', 0),
(58, 'Nutrition alert: Here’s what a 100 gram serving of cranberries contains', 5, 6, '<p>C<span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">ranberries are small, tart berries that are packed with various nutrients and offer several health benefits. Known for their bright, tart flavour, they are often consumed in juice form and are part of various desserts and salads. Cranberries are often regarded as a superfood owing to their abundant nutrients and</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/health/antioxidants-health-skin-benefits-free-radicals-foods-products-sources-ayurveda-side-effects-8097951/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px; background: 0px 0px rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">antioxidants</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">. Numerous studies have associated the nutrient profile of cranberries with a reduced likelihood of</span><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/health/simple-tips-to-prevent-utis-8423785/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px; background: 0px 0px rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;urinary tract infections (UTIs)</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px;\">, protection against specific types of cancer, enhanced immune function, and lowered blood pressure, among other benefits.</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Speaking with indianexpress.com, Guru Prasad Das, Senior Dietitian, CARE Hospitals, Bhubaneswar shared, “Cranberries can be enjoyed in various forms such as fresh, dried, frozen, or as juice. Including them as part of a diverse and balanced diet can contribute to overall health and well-being”.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:56:05', NULL, 1, 'Nutrition-alert:-Here’s-what-a-100-gram-serving-of-cranberries-contains', 'ff506a9c8352bf707107ab92e79a5f4d.jpg', 0),
(59, 'Understanding Panchakarma: An Ayurvedic treatment for the body, mind, and consciousness', 5, 3, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Ayurveda has a wide range of therapeutic techniques and practices for achieving physical and mental balance and wellness. Rooted in the principles of holistic healing,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/health/ayurvedic-lifestyle-changes-8263155/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Ayurveda</span>&nbsp;</a>offers unique treatment methods that address not only the physical aspects of health but also the mental, emotional and spiritual well-being. One such approach is&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">panchakarma</em>, which is a treatment programme to cleanse and rejuvenate the body, mind and consciousness. It is based on the principle that everything in this universe is made of the five basic elements of nature—ether, air, fire, water and earth.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">In the literal sense,&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">panchakarma</em>, derived from Sanskrit, translates to “five actions” or “five treatments”. “It is an excellent cleansing process that discharges stored&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/lifestyle/life-style/design-advice-less-toxic-life-8590700/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">toxins</span>&nbsp;</a>and restores the body’s natural healing abilities. It is a comprehensive system of purification methods used to cleanse the body of all unwanted waste and balance the body, mind and spirit,” Rajinder Dhamija, founder of Dharishah Ayurveda, said.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:57:31', NULL, 1, 'Understanding-Panchakarma:-An-Ayurvedic-treatment-for-the-body,-mind,-and-consciousness', 'fff0123b4f9e5c67858b9a4a39dbfb51.jpg', 0),
(60, 'Gujarat riots case: Supreme Court extends Teesta Setalvad’s interim bail till July 19', 6, 8, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Supreme Court on Wednesday extended the interim bail of activist Teesta Setalvad till further orders, the Bar and Bench reported.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The plea against Gujarat High Court order denying her bail while directing her to surrender before the authorities “immediately” will be heard and decided on July 19, the apex court said.</p><p class=\"first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Rejecting Setalvad’s bail plea last Saturday, the Gujarat HC observed that granting her bail would “deepen and widen communal polarisation” at a time when “we are heading towards progress of the country with an effort to strengthen communal harmony and brotherhood”.</p>', '2023-07-05 11:59:40', NULL, 1, 'Gujarat-riots-case:-Supreme-Court-extends-Teesta-Setalvad’s-interim-bail-till-July-19', 'bc579f05aa06d7da9156671ce27d687f.jpg', 0),
(61, 'MP admin razes illegal encroachment of accused who ‘urinated on tribal’', 6, 7, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">A day after&nbsp;Madhya Pradesh police arrested Pravesh Shukla,&nbsp;following a purported&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/india/video-shows-mp-man-urinating-on-tribal-under-cong-fire-cm-chouhan-says-book-culprit-under-nsa-8748961/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">video showing him urinating on a tribal man</span></a>&nbsp;in Sidhi district, the state administration bulldozed the illegal encroachment of the accused.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The police registered a case under IPC sections 294 (obscene acts and songs), 504 (intentional insult with intent to provoke breach of the peace) and the SC/ST (Prevention of Atrocities) Act against Shukla. It also slapped the<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/india/madhya-pradesh-man-urinating-tribal-arrested-8754002/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;National Security Act (NSA) on him</span></a>.</p>', '2023-07-05 12:01:18', NULL, 1, 'MP-admin-razes-illegal-encroachment-of-accused-who-‘urinated-on-tribal’', 'd95f35592302e474489dd3cf4e2366fe.jpg', 0),
(62, 'BJP welcomes Gujarat HC upholding Rahul conviction', 6, 7, '<p><div class=\"\" id=\"artmeterpv\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Merriweather, serif; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"></div></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Faustina, serif; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 19px; line-height: 28px; text-align: left; letter-spacing: 0.05px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">BJP on July 7 welcomed the<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/gujarat-high-court-dismisses-rahul-gandhis-plea-against-his-conviction-in-defamation-case/article67052520.ece\" target=\"_self\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; color: rgb(176, 0, 32) !important; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: inherit;\">Gujarat High Court’s order refusing to vacate a stay on Congress leade</a>r Rahul Gandhi’s conviction by a court in Surat in a case of criminal defamation, with BJP MP Ravi Shankar Prasad stating that it had become a “chronic habit” of the Congress leader to “abuse and defame” leaders and organisations.</p>', '2023-07-07 12:55:47', NULL, 1, 'BJP-welcomes-Gujarat-HC-upholding-Rahul-conviction', '8e4c5474e86bce93102235ff109e0c13.jpg', 0),
(63, 'Gujarat High Court dismisses Rahul Gandhi’s plea against his conviction in defamation case', 6, 7, '<div class=\"article-picture top-pic \" style=\"font-family: Merriweather, serif;\"><p class=\"caption\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Merriweather Sans&quot;, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.2px;\"><br></p></div><div id=\"content-body-67052520\" class=\"articlebodycontent col-xl-9 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12\" itemprop=\"articleBody\" style=\"font-family: Merriweather, serif; flex: 0 0 auto; width: 713.25px; max-width: 100%; float: right;\"><p style=\"font-family: Faustina, serif; margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 19px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.05px;\">The Gujarat High Court on July 7, 2023, refused to stay the conviction and suspend&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/modi-surname-remark-surat-court-convicts-rahul-gandhi-in-defamation-case/article66651933.ece\" target=\"_self\" style=\"font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; cursor: pointer; font-size: inherit; color: rgb(176, 0, 32) !important;\">two years jail term awarded to Congress leader Rahul&nbsp;Gandhi in the criminal defamation case</a>&nbsp;in which he has been sentenced to two years in jail by a court in Surat.</p><div><br></div><div class=\"\" id=\"artmeterpv\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-size: 16px;\"></div></div>', '2023-07-07 12:57:12', NULL, 1, 'Gujarat-High-Court-dismisses-Rahul-Gandhi’s-plea-against-his-conviction-in-defamation-case', 'b3daee78b83c6637101c20ef38a02a3b.jpg', 0);
INSERT INTO `tblposts` (`id`, `PostTitle`, `CategoryId`, `SubCategoryId`, `PostDetails`, `PostingDate`, `UpdationDate`, `Is_Active`, `PostUrl`, `PostImage`, `rating`) VALUES
(64, 'Praful Patel speaks: ‘Daughter had become fulcrum of Sharad Pawar’s actions, NCP’s future was at stake’', 6, 7, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Praful Patel,&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/bhujbal-patel-to-sharad-pawar-bless-us-accept-our-decision-8778929/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">who had been a trusted aide of Sharad Pawar</a></span>, and has now shifted allegiance to Ajit Pawar, acknowledged that only when you are in power can the works of party supporters, members, and the MLAs be fulfilled.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Speaking to&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Indian Express</em>, Patel said: “There are two main things that led to this decision… one, Sharad Pawar has himself in the past not been shy of allying with the BJP… two, his daughter has become the fulcrum of all his actions, and he has foisted his decision on everyone.”</p>', '2023-07-07 13:00:56', NULL, 1, 'Praful-Patel-speaks:-‘Daughter-had-become-fulcrum-of-Sharad-Pawar’s-actions,-NCP’s-future-was-at-stake’', 'd09002b2db562437449ad1d075cb69d9.jpg', 0),
(65, 'Rahul Gandhi’s appeal dismissed by Gujarat HC. What does this mean?', 6, 7, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The Gujarat High Court has dismissed Rahul Gandhi’s plea seeking a stay on his conviction in a criminal defamation case in which he has been sentenced to two years in prison.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">In April, a sessions court in Surat had dismissed the Congress leader’s appeal against the conviction order passed by a magistrate’s court in the previous month.</p><p class=\"first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">This means that Rahul, who had been elected to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/india/parliament-monsoon-session-live-updates-rajya-sabha-lok-sabha-8035871/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Lok Sabha</a>&nbsp;from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/elections/wayanad-lok-sabha-election-results/\" class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Wayanad</a>&nbsp;in Kerala in 2019, remains disqualified from Parliament. He can now go to the Supreme Court to appeal against the decision of the High Court.</p>', '2023-07-07 13:02:14', NULL, 1, 'Rahul-Gandhi’s-appeal-dismissed-by-Gujarat-HC.-What-does-this-mean?', 'b3daee78b83c6637101c20ef38a02a3b.jpg', 0),
(66, 'Behind CM washing feet, MP BJP worry over its hold on tribal ground', 6, 7, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">FROM&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/india/madhya-pradesh-govt-announces-rs-6-5-lakh-relief-for-tribal-man-who-was-urinated-on-8802695/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">WASHING the feet of Dashmat Rawat</span></a>, publicly apologising to him and granting him financial aid, to razing the house of accused Pravesh Shukla and charging him under the NSA, Chief Minister Shivraj Singh Chouhan has acted swiftly to contain the potential damage from the incident of urination on a tribal.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Adding to the pressure on the BJP was the Congress allegation that Shukla was a representative of the BJP MLA from Siddhi, Kedarnath Shukla. The MLA, who denied this, was among the BJP leaders who called on Rawat. After he faced protests during his visit to Rawat’s home in Siddhi, where he told the family all about the BJP government’s schemes for tribals, Chouhan stepped in to himself host Rawat in Bhopal</p>', '2023-07-07 13:03:07', NULL, 1, 'Behind-CM-washing-feet,-MP-BJP-worry-over-its-hold-on-tribal-ground', 'dea4cf2fe83457f9962eb2b7a5e2f436.jpg', 0),
(67, 'Delhi court summons BJP MP Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh in wrestlers’ sexual harassment case', 6, 7, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">A Delhi court Friday summoned&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/sport-others/brij-bhushan-the-bahubali-who-was-a-one-man-federation-8656679/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">BJP MP and outgoing Wrestling Federation of India (WFI) chief Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh</span></a>&nbsp;and Vinod Tomar after taking cognizance of the chargesheet filed against them for alleged sexual harassment, assault and stalking of six women wrestlers.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Additional Chief Metropolitan Magistrate Harjeet Singh Jaspal at the Rouse Avenue court directed Brij Bhushan and Tomar, the suspended assistant secretary of WFI, to appear on July 18.</p>', '2023-07-07 13:04:36', NULL, 1, 'Delhi-court-summons-BJP-MP-Brij-Bhushan-Sharan-Singh-in-wrestlers’-sexual-harassment-case', '9d1791b81ce7252dd475bde9a60b7010.jpg', 0),
(68, 'Maharashtra Politics News Live Updates: No split in NCP, majority in party supporting Ajit Pawar, says Praful Patel', 6, 7, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Maharashtra Political Crisis Live Updates (July 7):&nbsp;</span>Dismissing that there has been a split in the Nationalist Congress Party (NCP) Praful Patel, with Maharashtra Deputy CM Ajit Pawar by his side, said that more than 40 MLAs support them and hence they have sought the name and symbol of NCP from the election commission. “NCP held a meeting on June 30 in presence of many MLAs and MLCs at Devgiri. In that meeting, Ajit Pawar was chosen as the leader. He then appointed Praful Patel as national working president. This is not a split. Legislative and organisations back Ajit Pawar with majority,” he said.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Meanwhile, politics in Maharashtra has been a rapidly developing landscape over the last few weeks and it continued on Friday with Neelam Gorhe, a Member of Legislative Council from the Uddhav Thackeray-led Shiv Sena (UBT),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/mumbai/sanjay-raut-shiv-sena-mlas-ubt-eknath-shinde-8803916/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">joining the Eknath Shinde’s faction.</span></a>&nbsp;Gorhe is the third MLC from Shiv Sena (UBT) to switch sides. This came on a day when Shiv Sena (UBT) MP Sanjay Raut said that around 17-18 MLAs from the Eknath Shinde faction were in touch with them.</p>', '2023-07-07 13:05:33', NULL, 1, 'Maharashtra-Politics-News-Live-Updates:-No-split-in-NCP,-majority-in-party-supporting-Ajit-Pawar,-says-Praful-Patel', 'a1a9311a0cf89dc4cfc8cbd451886223jpeg', 0),
(69, 'Gender parity, equality will shape laws to bring in Uniform Civil Code', 6, 7, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">The principles of gender parity and equality before law are likely to shape the contours of the proposed&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/explained/explained-law/pm-modi-pushes-for-uniform-civil-code-how-it-can-impact-different-communities-8689361/\" class=\"\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\">Uniform Civil Code</a></span>, suggestions for which have been invited by the Law Commission of India from religious organisations and the public at large.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">Sources told&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">The Indian Express</em>&nbsp;that personal laws that clash with the constitutional mandate of gender equality will be examined and addressed in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/explained/explained-law/pm-modi-pushes-for-uniform-civil-code-how-it-can-impact-different-communities-8689361/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">the proposed UCC.</span></a>&nbsp;These could include laws that allow polygamy or prohibit equal rights for women in inheritance of property or in marriage.</p><p class=\"first_intro_para\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">It is likely that the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/india/muslim-law-board-on-ucc-majoritarian-morality-cant-supersede-minority-rights-8779762/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">UCC could be a string of tweaks</span></a>&nbsp;in existing laws to bring in broad uniformity in personal laws over a single code governing all aspects of marriage and inheritance, sources indicated.</p>', '2023-07-07 13:07:29', NULL, 1, 'Gender-parity,-equality-will-shape-laws-to-bring-in-Uniform-Civil-Code', 'f26ef01835a7136e8666fa2d622d60a1.jpg', 0),
(70, 'Blind movie review: Sonam Kapoor is ineffective in deadly dull film', 2, 12, '<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">ased on a 2011 Korean film of the same name, ‘Blind’ gives us the story of a young cop who has lost her sight in a terrible accident. Out of a job, and grieving over a death she has caused, Gia’s (<a href=\"https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/sonam-kapoor-attends-uk-pm-rishi-sunaks-reception-to-celebrate-uk-india-week-posts-pictures-8691914/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; color: rgb(52, 111, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: 700;\">Sonam Kapoor</span></a>) only solace is her seeing-eye dog Elsa, and the loving woman (Lillette Dubey) who runs the orphanage she grew up in, in Glasgow.</p><p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Droid Serif&quot;, serif; line-height: 28px;\">And then one day, a chance encounter with a sinister man turns her life upside down. Returning home from a visit to the orphanage, she gets into what she thinks is a taxi, but a few things make her uncomfortable: something moving in the boot (is that a human voice crying out?), the driver’s insistence that she drinks water (is the liquid safe?), and his all-round creepy behaviour. Local girls that have gone missing have been in the headlines: could it be this guy behind it?</p>', '2023-07-07 13:12:44', NULL, 1, 'Blind-movie-review:-Sonam-Kapoor-is-ineffective-in-deadly-dull-film', '527c76ade15c943388af108fd1357396.jpg', 0);

